  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "SOCIAL MEDIA PROJECT MANAGER",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Role Overview</strong></h3><p>We are looking for a <strong>strategic yet hands-on Social Media Project Manager</strong> to plan, execute, and manage social media campaigns across multiple platforms and brands. This role requires strong coordination skills, content planning expertise, and the ability to manage timelines, creatives, and performance outcomes in a fast-paced environment.<br /></p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Plan, manage, and execute <strong>end-to-end social media campaigns</strong> across platforms (Instagram, TikTok, Facebook, etc.)</p></li><li><p>Develop <strong>monthly content calendars</strong>, campaign timelines, and posting schedules</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with content creators, designers, videographers, and external agencies</p></li><li><p>Manage multiple social media projects simultaneously while meeting deadlines</p></li><li><p>Oversee content production from concept to publishing</p></li><li><p>Monitor performance metrics and provide <strong>campaign reports and insights</strong></p></li><li><p>Ensure brand consistency across all social media channels</p></li><li><p>Manage influencer collaborations, campaign briefs, and deliverables</p></li><li><p>Stay updated on social media trends, platform updates, and algorithm changes</p></li><li><p>Work closely with marketing and operations teams to support promotions, launches, and events<br /></p><h3><strong>Requirements & Qualifications</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Diploma or Bachelor’s Degree in <strong>Marketing, Communications, Media, or related field</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>2–5 years of experience</strong> in social media management or digital marketing</p></li><li><p>Proven experience managing <strong>social media projects and campaigns</strong></p></li><li><p>Strong understanding of social media platforms, analytics, and content trends</p></li><li><p>Experience working with <strong>multiple brands or accounts</strong> is a strong advantage</p></li><li><p>Excellent project management and organizational skills</p></li><li><p>Ability to manage timelines, priorities, and cross-functional stakeholders</p></li><li><p>Strong written communication and creative briefing skills</p></li><li><p>Familiar with tools such as <strong>Meta Business Suite, TikTok Business, scheduling tools, and analytics platforms</strong></p></li><li><p>Comfortable working in a fast-paced, deadline-driven environment<br /></p><h3><strong>Preferred Skills (Advantageous)</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Experience in <strong>beauty, lifestyle, retail, or F&B industries</strong></p></li><li><p>Basic knowledge of paid ads, influencer marketing, or content performance optimization</p></li><li><p>Experience working with creatives, agencies, or production teams</p></li><li><p>Strong eye for branding, aesthetics, and storytelling</p></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul>",
